getAmountIn(uint256,(uint256,uint256,uin.details: given an output amount of an asset and pair reserves, returns a required input amount of the other asset Formula: return = reserveIn * ( (reserveOut / (reserveOut - amountOut)) ^ (tokenWeightOut / tokenWeightIn) - 1) * (10000/ (10000 - swapFee)

params.amountOut: target reserve amount  reserveIn    source reserve balance  reserveOut    target reserve balance  tokenWeightIn     source reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  tokenWeightOut     target reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  swapFee                  swap fee of the conversion

getAmountOut(uint256,(uint256,uint256,ui.details: given an input amount of an asset and pair reserves, returns the maximum output amount of the other asset, Formula: return = reserveOut * (1 - (reserveIn * 10000 / (reserveIn * 10000 + amountIn * (10000 - swapFee))) ^ (tokenWeightIn / tokenWeightOut))

params.amountIn: source reserve amount  reserveIn    source reserve balance  reserveOut    target reserve balance  tokenWeightIn     source reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  tokenWeightOut     target reserve weight, represented in ppm (2-98)  swapFee                  swap fee of the conversion
